{"tid":214850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支聯會28公里長跑　悼六四28周年","createTime":"2017-04-24T04:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T05:07:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e1a30bc929148200b30e704b5a1361c301d0328","tid":214850,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:22:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19999514&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19999514%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170424&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25Ym6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=56b0d3d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19999514%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170424&h=2a29661e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19999514&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170424</a><br />\n<br />\n支聯會28公里長跑　悼六四28周年<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n支聯會成員昨參與長跑，途經銅鑼灣時代廣場。夏家朗攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】約60名支聯會成員昨早舉行全程28公里的「六四長跑」活動，悼念六四事件28周年，領跑的副主席蔡耀昌指，支聯會正就新的六四紀念館籌款及選址，至今尚欠200萬，冀市民在今年六四燭光集會積極捐款。<br />\n支聯會一眾成員昨早清晨6時多，先由位於石硤尾賽馬會創意藝術中心的六四臨時紀念館外出發，跑到尖沙嘴乘渡輪過海，其後跑到銅鑼灣時代廣場，在民主女神像前與秘書李卓人等其他成員會合後，經港大國殤之柱等地，跑到終點中聯辦。<br />\n參加者並將民主女神像搬至中聯辦外，手持菊花默哀一分鐘後，將鮮花放於中聯辦門前後散去。<br />\n<br />\n籌款建館欠200萬<br />\n<br />\n蔡耀昌指約有60人參與長跑活動，延續平反六四的決心，他跑至後段更一度抽筋。而原設於尖沙嘴的六四紀念館去年7月閉館後，正於石硤尾設立臨時紀念館，蔡耀昌指紀念館將於4月30日至6月15日開放，正物色更大的地方設立永久紀念館，暫時未有確實選址，但是設立永久館須籌款300萬，惟至今只籌得100萬，希望市民於今年六四燭光集會積極捐款。<br />\n■記者許偉賢"},{"pid":"c42d1452bf042d27feb10475204c0bc09a4ffb03","tid":214850,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:23:58.000Z","msg":"之前好似CAP左千萬整左個乜春紀念館啦<br />\n<br />\n依家又想CAP水？<br />\n<br />\n其實支聯會主要業務係咪炒樓？"},{"pid":"09bca38e00f5476ba2ace65b3b4914992f33e6eb","tid":214850,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:40:29.000Z","msg":"戇鳩支那會"},{"pid":"1c61c00e6d1bcabf6cd48d7d0a1a138c3d04e06f","tid":214850,"uid":1865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:54:46.000Z","msg":"支那會班老嘢連28米都跑唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d6735934f155f028fcb6048af7bd63722dc382","tid":214850,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:58:28.000Z","msg":"接力長跑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c88b47e52b8d19665279319c483ae73456b833f","tid":214850,"uid":3659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:59:39.000Z","msg":"1年跑多1公里<br />\n咁2047年果陣點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30706ca1664d9dc187642789c17987b60bd172f4","tid":214850,"uid":31652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T05:00:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1年跑多1公里<br />\n咁2047年果陣點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同渣馬合辦掛"},{"pid":"4d08a3f29e0007d29448a76abf204f3dec9b92ec","tid":214850,"uid":92315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T05:02:33.000Z","msg":"支那會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c73e23d2f1481ba1e85a1c17c8f67fb1724dbc","tid":214850,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T05:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1年跑多1公里<br />\n咁2047年果陣點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同渣馬合辦掛</blockquote><br />\n每人跑一公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}